<br>
    <p>theres this little indie game which i think is really underrated called The Multi Medium, where you play as an astronaut guy and travel between different worlds made of hand-drawn art, each in a different art form, like collage, acrylic, and stuff like that. i drew drawings in real life of some of the worlds, so here they are.</p>

