    <h1 id="motivationals">MOTIVATIONAL QUOTES</h1>
    <P>here's some motivational quotes for whatever, i'll try to add a new one every few days or so.</P>
    <br>
    <p>"The only thing predictable about life is its unpredictability." -Remy The Rat</p>
    <br>
    <p>"When things get hard, you'll always have someone by your side to help you." -Me!</p>
    <br>
    <p>“Compassion isn’t about solutions. It’s about giving all the love that you’ve got.” —Cheryl Strayed</p>
    <br>
    <br>
    <p>in the end, the whole point of this is to express a belief of mine that being kind really makes a difference.</p>
    <p>these motivational quotes are meant to make people here sort of think about whats around them, and this whole webpage thing is meant for people to reflect in general. 
    <p>being nice is honestly one of the most important thing you can do, and i know its a bit cheesy or whatever, but if you aren't already trying to spread kindness, i hope this music and stuffs can help you out. </p>
